													<h2 class="articletitle"><a href="http://liberalconspiracy.org/2014/04/17/cameron-is-playing-up-his-christianity-because-of-gay-marriage-not-poverty/" rel="bookmark">Cameron is playing up his Christianity because of gay marriage, not poverty</a></h2><br />
					<span id="authorarticle">by <strong>Sunny Hundal</strong>  &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><br />
					3:35 pm - April 17th 2014<br clear="all" /><br />
					
					<table cellspacing="0" cellspacing="0">
						<tr>
							<td><a href="http://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-count="horizontal" data-via="libcon" data-related="sunny_hundal">Tweet</a><script type="text/javascript" src="http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js"></script></td>
							<td style="width: 10px"> &nbsp; </td>

							<td><iframe src="//www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?href=http://liberalconspiracy.org/2014/04/17/cameron-is-playing-up-his-christianity-because-of-gay-marriage-not-poverty/&amp;send=false&amp;layout=button_count&amp;width=150&amp;show_faces=false&amp;action=recommend&amp;colorscheme=light&amp;font=arial&amp;height=21&amp;appId=135787006459018" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" style="border:none; overflow:hidden; width:150px; height:21px;" allowTransparency="true"></iframe></td>
							<td style="width: 10px"> &nbsp; </td>
							
							<td><g:plusone size="medium"></g:plusone></td>
							<td style="width: 10px"> &nbsp; </td>							

							<td><a href="http://www.tumblr.com/share" title="Share on Tumblr" style="display:inline-block; text-indent:-9999px; overflow:hidden; width:61px; height:20px; background:url('http://platform.tumblr.com/v1/share_2.png') top left no-repeat transparent;">Share on Tumblr</a></td>
						</tr>
